B%20Gebbia%2C%2044%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Gebbia%20and%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20created%20Gebbia's%20new%20role%20and%20the%20National%20Design%20Studio.%20In%20his%20order%2C%20Trump%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Btime%20to%20fill%20the%20digital%20potholes%20across%20our%20Nation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bupdate%20the%20Government's%20design%20language%20to%20be%20both%20usable%20and%20beautiful.%26quot%3B%20The%20national%20initiative%20would%20be%20called%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20by%20Design%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20order%2C%20federal%20agency%20chiefs%20will%20have%20to%20consult%20with%20Gebbia%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20the%20initiative%20and%20%26quot%3Bshall%20produce%20initial%20results%20by%20July%204%2C%202026.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGebbia%20told%20Axios%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20injustice%20that%20our%20interfaces%20are%20horribly%20out%20of%20date.%26quot%3B%20Government%20mobile%20apps%20and%20websites%20act%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfront%20door%20to%20the%20government%26quot%3B%20and%20should%20be%20as%20beautifully%20designed%20as%20platforms%20made%20by%20Apple%20and%20Airbnb%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20reason%20why%20our%20government%20can't%20be%20a%20standard%20for%20great%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebbia%20told%20Axios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGebbia%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20In%20February%2C%20Gebbia%20said%20he%20was%20joining%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20DOGE%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20first%20project%20at%20DOGE%20would%20be%20to%20improve%20the%20%26quot%3Bslow%20and%20paper-based%20retire