rfect%20curry%20puff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20%E2%80%94%20who%20run%20the%20Singapore-based%20curry%20puff%20business%20What%20The%20Puff%20%E2%80%94%20rolled%20out%20the%20pastry%20dough%2C%20stuffed%20it%20with%20a%20curry%20filling%2C%20pleated%20the%20edges%2C%20and%20fried%20it%20golden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20a%20crispy%2C%20buttery%2C%20and%20savory%20pastry%20that%20drew%20a%2015-person%20queue%20to%20their%20newest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-glamorous-job-flight-attendant-opened-nasi-lemak-stall-singapore-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehawker%20stall%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Singapore's%20northeastern%20Punggol%20neighborhood%20when%20Business%20Insider%20visited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20brothers%20fill%20the%20dough%20with%20the%20curry%20mix%20and%20fry%20it%20for%20about%20seven%20minutes%20until%20it's%20golden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6891cfa23d5881a51c1e9908%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20brothers%20fill%20the%20dough%20with%20the%20curry%20mix%20and%20fry%20it%20for%20about%20seven%20minutes%20until%20it's%20golden.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELim%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20finance%20sophomore%20at%20the%20Singapore%20University%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20started%20the%20curry%20puff%20business%20in%20December.%20Business%20is%20booming%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20already%20expanded%20to%20two%20other%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuggling%20college%20and%20a%20nascent%20business%20in%20a%20country%20known%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefused-to-work-office-job-started-stall-using-grandma-recipes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh%20food%20and%20beverage%20business%20failure%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20no%20easy%20task.%20He's%20had%20to%20forgo%20his%20social%20life%2C%20take%20calls%20from%20suppliers%20during%20classes%2C%20and%20work%20until%20his%20hands%20ache.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he's%20hoping%20the%20business%20takes%20off%20so%20well%20that%20he'll%20never%20have%20to%20set%20foot%20in%20an%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8569ea2-04f5-4ea9-b5c0-8f5bc41e329d%5C%22%3ERaised%20by%20hawker-loving%20parents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223735%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20was%20a%20long%20queue%20of%20about%2015%20people%20when%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20stall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6891cdfcf748d8c055f6e086%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222801%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20was%20a%20long%20queue%20of%20about%2015%20people%20when%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20stall%20post-lunch.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20said%20his%20mother%20and%20father%20supported%20him%20juggling%20a%20food%20business%20and%20his%20studies.%20His%20father%20even%20suggested%20he%20drop%20out%20of%20college%20to%20build%20up%20What%20The%20Puff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20unconventional%20advice%2C%20but%20he's%20a%20pretty%20unconventional%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20have%20always%20been%20in%20the%20F%26amp%3BB%20industry%2C%20he%20said.%20They%20ran%20a%20laksa%20steamboat%20restaurant%20in%20the%202010s%20and%20later%20opened%20a%20Teochew%20porridge%20hawker%20stall%20when%20Lim%20was%20in%20middle%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20helped%20with%20cashiering%20and%20loading%20toppings%20on%20porridge%20on%20the%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9862d81-4278-4312-97fa-93a8777f25cd%5C%22%3ESelling%20thousands%20of%20curry%20puffs%20daily%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223842%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20freshly%20fried%20puff%20was%20filled%20with%20a%20potato%2C%20chicken%2C%20and%20egg%20curry%20mix%20and%20had%20a%20buttery%20and