r%20going%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he's%20decided%20that%20he's%20not%20going%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f57f7d5-3d87-4e20-b366-82bdf8d5133a%5C%22%3EA%20three-year%20runway%20for%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20said%20he%20gave%20himself%20until%20graduation%20to%20make%20this%20business%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20now%20to%20graduation%2C%20I%20have%20around%20three%20years%2C%20so%20that's%20my%20runway%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20three%20years%20to%20build%20this%20into%20something%20which%20hopefully%20I%20can%20do%20full%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20strenuous%2C%20he%20prefers%20it%20to%20a%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20that%20I%20can%20be%20running%20errands%2C%20doing%20my%20degree%2C%20and%20having%20flexible%20hours%2C%20which%20feels%20better%20than%20sitting%20down%20and%20being%20desk-bound%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20when%20he%20gets%20good%20feedback%20from%20his%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20me%20this%20great%20sense%20of%20fulfillment%20when%20people%20leave%20good%20reviews%20or%20tell%20us%20in%20person%20that%20they%20enjoyed%20the%20curry%20puffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-sophomore-started-booming-side-hustle-making-curry-puffs-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756083844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689c34a0cfc04e97619b4fe3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-sophomore-started-booming-side-hustle-making-curry-puffs-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20year%2C%20Lim%20Yuan%20Ming%20started%20curry%20puff%20business%20that%20took%20off%20rapidly.%20Now%2C%20he%20ho