urselves%20into%20it.%20I%20work%20harder%20on%20that%20than%20I've%20ever%20worked%20on%20many%20jobs%2C%20even%20when%20I%20was%20in%20corporate%20life.%20This%20costs%20us%20money%20in%20software%20and%20website%20fees%20to%20run%2C%20but%20people%20pay%20to%20do%20their%20hobbies%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20we%20find%20it%20incredibly%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We're%20also%20writing%20a%20book%20on%20getting%20to%20financial%20freedom%20and%20just%20worked%20with%20a%20team%20to%20produce%20a%20music%20album%20with%20songs%20about%20index%20funds%2C%20compounding%2C%20and%20the%204%25%20FI%20rule%20in%20different%20music%20genres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20always%20hit%20a%20balance%2C%20and%20I%20have%20overcommitted%20us%20sometimes%2C%20but%20here%20are%20three%20things%20we%20do%20to%20ensure%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early-saving-loneliness-retreat-bali-making-friends-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20remains%20fun%20and%20burnout-free%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256fe9895-5486-49bd-9142-ad7778ac8093%5C%22%3E1.%20Does%20it%20make%20us%20want%20to%20say%20hell%20yes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKatie%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Our%20rough%20rule%20now%20is%20that%20it's%20either%20a%20hell%20yes%20or%20it's%20a%20no.%20If%20you%20fill%20your%20time%20with%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%26quot%3B%20then%20you'll%20have%20a%20life%20of%20maybes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20had%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20say%20no%2C%20even%20to%20big%20conferences%2C%20because%20we%20did%20not%20think%20there%20was%20room%20for%20us%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20and%20drive%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20focus%20and%20let%20go%20of%2010%20or%2012%20different%20opportunities%20this%20year%20because%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20space%20for%20bigger%20impact%20commitments%20that%20can%20help%20more