%2C%20for%20writing%20our%20book%20or%20the%20speaking%20tour%20we%20did%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20we%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20and%20then%20we%20have%20time%20to%20go%20back%20to%20our%20travel%20or%20other%20hobbies.%20Our%20FI%20course%20is%20also%20designed%20to%20end%20in%20three%20months%20and%20give%20us%20back%20our%20time%20and%20independence%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20being%20free%2C%20we%20start%20thinking%20of%20what%20fun%20and%20crazy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-planning-journey-nyc-healthcare-divorce-health-family-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ething%20we%20could%20do%20next%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpriortizing-hobbies-in-retirement-fire-financial-independence-alan-katie-donegan-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756080001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a55327cfc04e97619bad41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpriortizing-hobbies-in-retirement-fire-financial-independence-alan-katie-donegan-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20FIRE%2C%20Alan%20and%20Katie%20Donegan%20have%20traveled%20too%20much%20and%20overcommitted%20to%20projects.%20They%20shared%20three%20ways%20to%20avoid%20burnout%20in%20retirement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpriortizing-hobbies-in-retirement-fire-financial-independence-alan-katie-donegan-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20behind%20the%20passion%20of%20Love%20Island%20USA's%20Nigerian%20fanbase%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756079065000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbc