he'll%20be%20experiencing%20a%20lot%20as%20a%20new%20mom.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20I%20challenged%20myself%20to%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20strangers%2C%20try%20new%20foods%20(like%20r%C3%B6sti%2C%20a%20crispy%20shredded%20potato%20cake)%2C%20and%20wander%20around%20town%20with%20no%20map%20or%20GPS%20to%20guide%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cec1589a-e844-4dc5-9cfd-591c77ec0d2d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20overcame%20a%20lifelong%20fear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrindelwald%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20face%20my%20lifelong%20fear%20of%20heights.%20On%20my%20first%20day%2C%20I%20rode%20the%20Eiger%20Express%20%E2%80%94%20a%20high-speed%20cable%20car%20%E2%80%94%20followed%20by%20a%20train%20to%20the%20highest%20railway%20station%20in%20all%20of%20Europe%20at%2011%2C332%20feet%20above%20sea%20level.%20That%20night%2C%20I%20took%20the%20steep%20funicular%20ride%202%2C500%20feet%20up%20to%20Harder%20Kulm%20in%20Interlaken.%20And%20on%20my%20third%20day%2C%20I%20took%20a%20stroll%20along%20the%20First%20Cliff%20Walk%20%E2%80%94%20a%20narrow%2C%20cliff-hugging%20walkway%20148%20feet%20off%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20knees%20may%20have%20trembled%20at%20times%2C%20but%20safely%20accomplishing%20these%20feats%20paid%20off.%20On%20my%20final%20day%2C%20I%20strutted%20with%20surprising%20ease%20down%20the%20path%20at%20the%20984-foot%20Glacier%20Gorge.%20I%20was%20even%20able%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20railing%20and%20stare%20down%20into%20the%20canyon%20below%20while%20snapping%20photos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3991355-6c7e-4ced-b922-9b637771c3aa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20took%20time%20for%20self-care%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20nausea%20to%20unexpected%20mood%20swings%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%