%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheating-tech-interviews-soaring-managers-lost-gen-ai-chatgpt-coding-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20hunting%20for%20software%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFonzi%20connects%20candidates%20with%20employers%20and%20requires%20companies%20to%20disclose%20salaries%20upfront.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraditional%20recruiting%20is%20often%20slow%20and%20inefficient%2C%20Fonzi's%20CEO%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20Bardelli%20knew%20right%20away%20that%20his%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-tips-flexibility-career-advancement-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20hunt%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20going%20to%20be%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20software%20engineer%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20that%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20role%2C%20he%20didn't%20hear%20from%20former%20colleagues%20with%20offers%20to%20come%20work%20with%20them%20again%2C%20as%20he%20had%20during%20past%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20different%2C%20and%20definitely%20drier%20than%20I've%20seen%20it%20be%20in%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Bardelli%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20he%20heard%20from%20a%20recruiter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffonzi.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFonzi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20matches%20engineers%20with%20startups%20and%20tech%20companies%2C%20Bardelli%20was%20intrigued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20completed%20a%20profile%20and%20applied%20to%20what%20Fonzi%20calls%20Match%20Day%2C%20the%20process%20through%20which%20employers%20can%20meet%20with%20candidates.%20Three%20of%20the%2014%20participating%20companies%20offered%20Bardelli%20interviews.%20That%20allowed%20him%20to%20sidestep%20a%20protracted%20job%20search%20and%20many%20of%20the%20headaches%20that%20go%20along%20with%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20in%20tech%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-software-engineers-coders-bad-market-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elayoffs%20and%20sluggish%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20translated%20to%20job%20searches%20marked%20by%20seemingly%20endless%20rounds%20of%20applying.%20Letting%20an%20employer%20come%20to%20you%20likely%20offers%20an%20appealing%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20hope%20of%20Yang%20Mou%2C%20Fonzi's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-doesnt-post-open-jobs-gets-too-many-resumes-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraditional%20recruiting%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20inefficient%20and%20%26quot%3Bbroken%20for%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMou%20said%20this%20results%20in%20candidates%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20trying%20to%20determine%20whether%20a%20company%20is%20a%20good%20fit.%20When%20candidates%20do%20land%20interviews%2C%20he%20said%2C%20they%20often%20repeat%20themselves%20in%20similar%20conversations%20with%20multiple%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-tips-recruiters-execs-applicants-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20ultimate%20guide%20to%20getting%20a%20job%3A%20Recruiters%2C%20job%20seekers%2C%20and%20execs%20reveal%20top%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-opening-apply-fast-linkedin-indeed-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20hidden%20power%20of%20applying%20quickly%20to%20your%20dream%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployers%2C%20for%20their%20part%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20flooded%20with%20applicants%2C%26quot%3B%20Mou%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20put%20up%20a%20job%20post%2C%20you%20get%201%2C000%20applicants%20in%2024%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20try%20to%20make%20the%20whole%20process%20more%20palatable%2C%20Mou%20said%2C%20Fonzi%20takes%20candidates%20who%20know%20what%20they%20want%20in%20a%20new%20role%20and%20connects%20them%20with%20employers%20that%20have%20real%20jobs%20and%20%26quot%3Bsane%20hiring%20processes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20going%20to%20drag%20it%20out%20for%20three%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278aa315b-b099-45d0-87b3-d204372ade86%5C%22%3ECommitting%20to%20a%20minimum%20salary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20seeking%20talent%20through%20Fonzi%20are%20required%20to%20commit%20to%20minimum%20salaries%20upfront%20so%20that%20candidates%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20through%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20only%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20pay%20won't%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMou%20said%20engineers%20must%20complete%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20selective%26quot%3B%20application%20process%20before%20being%20matched%20with%20an%20employer.%20Part%20of%20that%20involves%20a%20brief%20exchange%20with%20Fonzi's%20AI%20interviewer.%20The%20agent%20can%20handle%20complex%20conversations%2C%20including%20understanding%20the%20candidate's%20technical%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20an%20AI%20agent%2C%20Mou%20said%2C%20can%20be%20helpful%20for%20busy%20engineers%20who%20might%20want%20to%20wait%20until%20after%20the%20workday%20to%20complete%20that%20part%20of%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20infinite%20patience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20ramble%20for%2015%20minutes%20and%20it%20won't%20cut%20you%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFonzi%20combines%20the%20AI%20interview%20with%20candidates'%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20additional%20details%20on%20their%20work%20histories%2C%20and%20personal%20preferences%20such%20as%20where%20they%20want%20to%20work%20and%20for%20what%20type%20of%20company.%20A%20Fonzi%20recruiter%20then%20talks%20by%20phone%20with%20those%20who%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20good%20fit.%20From%20there%2C%20Fonzi%20invites%20top%20candidates%20to%20take%20part%20in%20Match%20Day%20and%20assigns%20each%20candidate%20a%20recruiter%20to%20work%20with%20during%20the%20job%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conversations%20with%20the%20recruiter%20help%20to%20identify%20important%20attributes%2C%20Mou%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20they%20a%20capable%20communicator%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20want%20to%20work%20with%20this%20person%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discussions%20also%20help%20reveal%20more%20than%20what's%20on%20someone's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20said%20Bec%20Bliss%2C%20a%20recruiter%20who%20is%20Fonzi's%20head%20of%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20folks%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20they%20love%2C%20what%20they're%20good%20at%2C%20what%20they%20want%20to%20be%20doing%20turns%20them%20into%20the%20full%2C%203D%20candidate%20instead%20of%20a%20sheet%20of%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20month%2C%20Fonzi%20AI%20has%20Match%20Day%20for%20engineers%20seeking%20in-person%20and%20hybrid%20roles%20in%20the%20New%20York%20area%20and%20for%20remote%20roles%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20company%20plans%20to%20offer%20in-person%20and%20hybrid%20roles%20in%20San%20Fransicso%20in%20October%20and%20other%20cities%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFonzi%20is%20free%20for%20job%20seekers%20and%20charges%20a%20fee%20of%2018%25%20of%20the%20base%20salary%20if%20a%20company%20makes%20a%20hire.%20Because%20the%20business%20model%20is%20only%20about%20three%20months%20old%2C%20the%20company%20hasn't%20released%20stats%20on%20how%20many%20workers%20employers%20have%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c662ed22-ed7e-4605-a6ed-88b5e443d7b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Happy%20to%20have%20any%20matches'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Bardelli%2C%20the%20lackluster%20job%20market%20meant%20that%20after%20leaving%20a%20prior%20role%2C%20he%20expected%20to%20have%20to%20brush%20up%20on%20his%20interviewing%20and%20networking%20skills%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20the%20network%20he'd%20built%20up%20over%20about%2020%20years%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20hitting%20the%20market%20cold%2C%26quot%3B%20Bardelli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetworking%2C%20many%20recruiters%20insist%2C%20is%20still%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20ways%20to%20find%20a%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20get%20past%20the%20screening%20software%20that%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frejected-job-but-got-hired-contacted-hiring-manager-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emany%20job%20seekers%20hate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%2C%20if%20there's%20not%20much%20hiring%20going%20on%2C%20the%20search%20can%20be%20tough%20even%20when%20you're%20plugged%20in%2C%20as%20Bardelli%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20like%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20hiring%20has%20kind%20of%20dried%20up%20at%20our%20company%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20comments%20he%20heard%20from%20industry%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Bardelli%20settled%20on%20an%20employer%20he%20connected%20with%20through%20Fonzi%20and%20started%20his%20new%20role%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20going%20into%20the%20process%20with%20Fonzi%2C%20he%20wondered%20whether%20employers%20would%20like%20what%20he%20had%20to%20offer%2C%20though%20he%20was%20optimistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20my%20skills%20were%20relevant%20enough%20that%20maybe%20I'd%20get%20a%20match%20or%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20Bardelli%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20happy%20to%20have%20any%20matches%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20job%20search%3F%20Contact%20th