tricts%20for%20families%20in%20the%2050%20largest%20US%20metros.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20school%20districts%20considered%20had%20at%20least%20100%20homes%20for%20sale%20between%20May%20and%20July%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20top%20school%20districts%2C%20homeowners%20pay%20well%20above%20the%20typical%20home%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20parents%20are%20willing%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile%20for%20their%20kids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fannual-cost-to-raise-a-child-each-state-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20matter%20the%20extra%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20true%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20education.%20For%20many%20parents%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fextreme-moves-gifts-parents-use-get-kids-into-prestigious-preschools-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equality%20of%20local%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20and%20a%20big%20factor%20in%20homebuying%20decisions.%20Often%2C%20getting%20into%20the%20best%20schools%20also%20means%20paying%20a%20premium%20to%20live%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20most%20popular%20school%20districts%20for%20families%20in%20the%2050%20largest%20US%20metros%2C%20Realtor.com%20analyzed%20the%20number%20of%20views%20listings%20on%20its%20website%20received%20from%20out-of-market%20shoppers%20between%20May%20and%20July%202025.%20The%20study%20focused%20on%20districts%20with%20at%20least%20100%20homes%20for%20sale%20during%20this%20period%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20nearby%20public%20school%20rated%208%20or%20higher%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20website%20GreatSchools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERealtor.com%20found%20that%20while%20the%20nation's%20top-rated%20school%20districts%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20country%2C%20many%20share%20one%20thing%20in%20common%3A%20homeowners%20in%20these%20districts%20pay%20much%20more%20for%20a%20typical%20