usinessinsider.com%2Ftypes-of-communication-styles-improve-friendship-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunication%20style%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20more%20talkative%20than%20yours%2C%20or%20they%20might%20need%20more%20support%20during%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20should%20also%20find%20time%20to%20ask%20you%20questions%20back%20and%20remember%20details%20about%20your%20life.%20Otherwise%2C%20you're%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-friend-is-an-energy-vampire-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenergy%20vampire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drained%20from%20listening%20to%20your%20friend's%20vents%20without%20ever%20getting%20the%20floor%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202735a03-19a1-4d81-ad7b-a0d281a70885%5C%22%3E2.%20They%20tear%20you%20down%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20'brutal%20honesty'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGreat%20friendships%20will%20occasionally%20involve%20telling%20each%20other%20what%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kirmayer%20said%20there's%20a%20difference%20between%20sharing%20hard%20truths%20and%20insulting%20your%20friend's%20life%20choices%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20being%20honest!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20the%20truest%20sense%20of%20belonging%20and%20connection%20when%20we%20feel%20seen%2C%20heard%2C%20and%20appreciated%20for%20who%20we%20actually%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirmayer%20said.%20If%20you%20constantly%20get%20told%20you're%20doing%20something%20wrong%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20can%20end%20up%20feeling%20like%20that%20friendship%20is%20conditional%20on%20our%20willingness%20or%20ability%20to%20mold%20ourselves%20into%20who%20they%20want%20us%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20they're%20taking%20jabs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubtle-signs-your-friend-is-jealous-of-you-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eout%20of%20jealousy%3C