ther%20low%20risk%20or%20when%20a%20perfect%20decision%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20make.%20It's%20a%20great%20practice%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20messiness%20of%20overthinking%20and%20move%20to%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Granahan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fine%20line%20the%20practice%20walks%2C%20though%2C%20is%20with%20impulsivity%20or%20with%20higher%20risk%20decisions%20%5Bwhere%5D%20you%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20are%20taking%20in%20all%20relevant%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20it's%20easiest%20to%20start%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmens-morning-routines-set-up-for-success-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edaily%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20the%20day's%20plans%20or%20meals.%20But%20then%2C%20I%20get%20the%20most%20impact%20from%20this%20rule%20by%20applying%20it%20to%20situations%20I've%20been%20overthinking%20for%20longer%20than%20I%20know%20I%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c83d28ad-f9f2-4f06-ba80-a89d924d6fcf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20paralysis%20of%20making%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Oster%2C%20a%20parenting%20data%20scientist%2C%20once%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fparentdata.org%2Ftheres-no-secret-option-c%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecret%20option%20C%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20An%20imperfect%20decision%20is%20better%20than%20the%20paralysis%20of%20making%20a%20perfect%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20having%20five%20kids%20meant%20each%20decision%20carried%20such%20weight%2C%20with%20little%20lives%20and%20futures%20depending%20on%20making%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20one%2C%20that%20I'd%20constantly%20be%20scanning%20for%20that%20better%20option%20C.%20Often%2C%20usually%2C%20there%20just%20isn't%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20next%20time%20I%20find%20myself%20searching%20for%20the%20right%20choice%2C%20or%20a%20bet