tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20has%20helped%20Ancestry%20streamline%20its%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECTO%20Sriram%20Thiagarajan%20said%20its%20in-house%20AI%20tech%20cut%20the%20time%20needed%20to%20scan%20public%20records.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAncestry%20is%20beta%20testing%20a%20new%20AI%20feature%20called%20Audio%20Stories.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20say%20Ancestry's%20database%20is%20vast%20would%20be%20an%20understatement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20collected%20over%2065%20billion%20records%20across%2080-plus%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-are-using-ai-generative-ai-daily-tasks-automation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESriram%20Thiagarajan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20and%20technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BJust%20to%20give%20a%20scale%2C%20that's%20about%2010%2C000%20terabytes%20of%20data%20on%20our%20platform%20that%20we%20use%20to%20provide%20discoveries%20to%20our%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Utah-based%20genealogy%20company%2C%20founded%20in%201983%2C%20collects%20records%20to%20help%20people%20unearth%20their%20family%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20records%20include%20birth%2C%20death%2C%20marriage%2C%20census%2C%20military%2C%20land%2C%20immigration%2C%20and%20newspapers.%20Ancestry%2C%20which%20also%20offers%20consumer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fancestrydna-vs-23andme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDNA%20test%20kits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20collaborates%20with%20institutions%20like%20the%20National%20Archives%20and%20Records%20Administration%20to%20collect%20that%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20daunting%20caveat%20with%20a%20trove%20that%20size%2C%20though%3A%20organizing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiagarajan%20said%20Ancestry%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-ai-linkedin-vp-built-launched-app-weeks-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleveraging%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emachine%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20the%20Herculean%20task%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e5178ae-34eb-47a6-bac0-19602dd08080%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStreamlining%20with%20computer%20vision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20joined%20Ancestry's%20team%20in%202017%2C%20Thiagarajan%20said%20the%20company%20had%20just%20begun%20exploring%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20an%20effective%20and%20efficient%20way%20to%20digitize%20content%20that%20we%20acquire%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Thiagarajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAncestry%20used%20to%20scan%20the%20records%2C%20then%20outsource%20operations%20to%20manually%20index%20and%20key%20relevant%20fields.%20That%20information%20was%20uploaded%20into%20Ancestry's%20database%20before%20software%20programs%20established%20relationships%20between%20people%2C%20locations%2C%20or%20other%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%2015%20or%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20we%20digitized%20the%201940%20census%2C%20it%20took%20us%20about%20nine%20months%20to%20do%20it%20in%20a%20manual%20way%20at%2010%20times%20the%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20Thiagarajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sent%20the%20Ancestry%20team%20searching%20for%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20said%2C%20'Why%20don't%20we%20apply%20computer%20vision%20AI%20techniques%20to%20automatically%20digitize%20content%20without%20manual%20intervention%3F'%20Thiagarajan%20said.%20%26quot%3BFast%20forward%20to%20the%202021%20timeframe%2C%20we%20used%20our%20own%20proprietary%20handwriting%20recognition%20computer%20vision%20technologies%2C%20and%20we%20compressed%20the%20time%20to%20market%20to%20under%20nine%20days%20from%20nine%20months%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiagarajan%20said%20Ancestry%20has%20since%20expanded%20that%20technology%20to%20process%20other%20record%20types%2C%20but%20said%20humans%20still%20review%20AI%20results%20%26quot%3Bas%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20built%20some%20automated%20controls%20and%20systems%20that%20certainly%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20we%20need%20to%20spend%20checking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20extra%20careful%20in%20making%20sure%20that%20what%20we%20produce%20using%20AI%20is%20grounded%20in%20truth.%20Grounded%20in%20facts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiagarajan%20added%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bextent%20to%20which%20we%20do%20it%20now%20versus%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20has%20certainly%20improved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20consumers%20come%20to%20our%20platform%20looking%20for%20stories%20about%20their%20ancestors%2C%20we%20want%20to%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20records%20we%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce851fc1-c504-462c-a8f8-f17bc1ff0150%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAncestry%20is%20beta%20testing%20a%20new%20AI%20feature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20implementing%20AI%20into%20the%20backend%2C%20Ancestry%20has%20deployed%20several%20features%20for%20users%2C%20including%20its%20handwriting%20recognition%20tool.%20It%20began%20testing%20an%20AI%20assistant%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20Thiagarajan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Ancestry%20began%20beta%20testing%20an%20AI-powered%20feature%20called%20Audio%20Stories%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20turn%20records%20into%20a%20narrative%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20AI%20can%20understand%20the%20context%20between%20the%20printed%20material%2C%20the%20image%2C%20and%20the%20handwritten%20narrative%2C%20and%20tie%20it%20all%20together%20into%20a%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Thiagarajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there's%20no%20official%20launch%20date%20for%20Audio%20Stories%20yet%2C%20Ancestry%20is%20already%20thinking%20above%20and%20beyond%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDown%20the%20road%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20add%20sight%2C%20sound%2C%20motion%2C%20and%20video%20storytelling%2C%26quot%3B%20Thiagarajan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ancestry-uses-ai-records-processing-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756028101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a9f33d194a2d49b8af125d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ancestry-uses-ai-records-processing-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancestry%20has%2065%20billion%20records%20from%20more%20than%2080%20countries.%20The%20company's%20CTO%20said%20that's%20about%20about%2010%2C000%20terabytes%20of%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ancestry-uses-ai-records-processing-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20than%2030%20jihadists%20killed%20in%20air%20strikes%2C%20Nigerian%20military%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756027722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0076%2Flive%2Ffe1bf060-80c2-11f0-ab3e-bd52082cd0ae.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcq58123z814o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Concern%20is%20mounting%20about%20%26quot%3Bwar-time%20levels%20of%20slaughter%26quot%3B%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20including%20a%20resurgence%20of%20jihadist%20activity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%