to%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20access%20large%20mills%20and%20do%20not%20have%20full%20control%20over%20how%20or%20when%20their%20paddy%20is%20processed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Assad%20explains.%20SEMA%E2%80%99s%20solution%20puts%20that%20power%20back%20in%20the%20village%2C%20providing%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20farmer-first%20machine%20that%20can%20work%20with%20small%20batches.%20This%20approach%20reduces%20transport%20hassles%2C%20prevents%20losses%2C%20and%20cuts%20operational%20costs.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20integrating%20solar%20energy%20makes%20the%20solution%20both%20sustainable%20and%20aligned%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20wider%20renewable%20energy%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SEMA%E2%80%99s%20solution%20puts%20the%20power%20of%20rice%20milling%20back%20in%20the%20village%2C%20providing%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20farmer-first%20machine%20that%20can%20work%20with%20small%20batches%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C