20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20to%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInnovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20often%20remain%20isolated%20if%20they%20do%20not%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%20%E2%80%9COur%20role%20was%20to%20create%20those%20connections%2C%20making%20sure%20these%20technologies%20reach%20the%20farmers%20who%20need%20them%20most%2C%20backed%20by%20appropriate%20finance%2C%20supportive%20policy%2C%20and%20local%20demonstration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECEEW%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20were%20crucial%20in%20enabling%20end-user%20financing%20options%20for%20farmers%20who%20lacked%20collateral.%20They%20also%20organised%20demonstrations%20within%20villages%20to%20build%20trust%20and%20show%20the%20value%20of%20the%20mills%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20closely%20with%20financial%20institutions%20to%20introduce%20mechanisms%20like%20First%20Loss%20Default%20Guarantees.%20These%20tools%20reduce%20the%20risk%20lenders%20face%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20farmers%20with%20limited%20assets%20to%20access%20credit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CEEW%20helps%20unlock%20financing%2C%20raise%20awareness%2C%20and%20link%20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20to%20government%20schemes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook